{"tid":1769772,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【紐約時報】華為在中囯失去了民心","createTime":"2019-12-05T06:21:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-09T11:52:47.000Z","uid":131691,"like":42,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"64450986011419a947ec99070377b7271619be55","tid":1769772,"uid":131691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T06:21:55.000Z","msg":"英文原版：<a href=\"https://www.nytimes.com/2019/12/04/technology/huawei-china-backlash.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2019%2F12%2F04%2Ftechnology%2Fhuawei-china-backlash.html&d=nBH2CsHB%2BCaOzcOtxJw1eyHJFIlRN37b%2BuZTNWj4Tkw%3D&h=ccb016e9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.nytimes.com/2019/12/04/technology/huawei-china-backlash.html</a><br />\n中文版：<a href=\"https://cn.nytimes.com/technology/20191205/huawei-china-backlash/zh-hant/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcn.nytimes.com%2Ftechnology%2F20191205%2Fhuawei-china-backlash%2Fzh-hant%2F&d=nBH2CsHB%2BCaOzcOtxJw1eyHJFIlRN37b%2BuZTNWj4Tkw%3D&h=69a42f18\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://cn.nytimes.com/technology/20191205/huawei-china-backlash/zh-hant/</a><br />\n<br />\n全文精髓：<br />\n社群媒體上的憤怒也顯示出中國中產階級成員新的不安全感，他們從未經歷過經濟衰退，而且一直以為自己比低收入的農民工得到了更多保護。人們說，他們在李洪元身上看到自己。<br />\nThe anger on social media was also indicative of new insecurity among members of China&rsquo;s middle class, who have never experienced an economic downturn and have always thought they had more protections than lower-paid migrant workers. People said they could see themselves in Mr. Li.<br />\n 「打破了廣大中產『我學習優秀，一心工作，不問世事』就能被國家善待的中國夢，」一位部落客在微博上寫道。<br />\n&ldquo;Many middle-class Chinese used to believe that if they went to good schools, worked hard and cared little about the current affairs they would be able to realize their Chinese dreams,&rdquo; a blogger wrote on Weibo. &ldquo;Now their dreams are in tatters.&rdquo;<br />\n華為拒絕對公眾的反應發表評論。<br />\nHuawei declined to comment on the public response.<br />\n<br />\n==================<br />\n<br />\n應用於香港，其實有一班偏藍人嘅心態都係一樣：「收成期，唔好搞咁多嘢，專心做嘢，我討厭政治」。<br />\n<br />\n對策好簡單：令到佢哋嘅利益受損，佢哋自然就會出於自私，自然歸邊。<br />\n<br />\n簡單而言：攬炒。"},{"pid":"a994cbb2abc4ad8586d8aa6567901286762d30c7","tid":1769772,"uid":36088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T06:22:34.000Z","msg":"Up"},{"pid":"219055931b9fc6c79ec5bb25a2d2a07fd0eacbc1","tid":1769772,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T06:23:54.000Z","msg":"難道黑暗兵法回血劍<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89166e33c2c4ab644209bebaf27a5fec93d96fa7","tid":1769772,"uid":86509,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T06:27:57.000Z","msg":"歷史都係<br />\n一窮冇飽飯食就會作亂<br />\n享受慣就接受唔到自己要捱窮"},{"pid":"aebb03a110a14e1354a5d6b18fbfa1313fe5f81c","tid":1769772,"uid":79117,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T06:30:36.000Z","msg":"捧殺？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f18c6aabc9c043ffd008c42a7a38142626a15e3","tid":1769772,"uid":37722,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T06:32:26.000Z","msg":"一向我都話經濟攬炒先有出路"},{"pid":"9a97c9c2769e32d1f34071074fcc027252855fd6","tid":1769772,"uid":61282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T06:33:03.000Z","msg":"要令政治找上佢哋，但可能佢哋會政治覺醒，然後全力支持親共派止暴制亂，覺得咁先可以令香港回復平靜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e821592e579ef456ea276018be408ecea9b72ede","tid":1769772,"uid":131691,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"9a97c9c2769e32d1f34071074fcc027252855fd6","tid":1769772,"uid":61282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T06:33:03.000Z","msg":"要令政治找上佢哋，但可能佢哋會政治覺醒，然後全力支持親共派止暴制亂，覺得咁先可以令香港回復平靜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T06:37:29.000Z","msg":"無所謂，佢哋根本係出於自私，唔會有咩實質支持，只係講幾句跟住做free rider<br />\n當政權維穩打到自己，或維穩開始失敗，佢哋就會投誠<br />